imgDesc.text: Every now and then, new visitors of great skill will arrive at The Cat's Tail seeking worthy rivals in a game of cards. Face and overcome them in matches to earn <color=#ffe14b>Player EXP and Lucky Coins</color> <color=#ece5d8>.</color>
